Seven Days Live captures Poison (Bret Michaels, Bobby Dall, Rikki Rockett and Richie Kotzen) at the height of their international success with a full show recorded at Londons Hammersmith Apollo in 1993. Featuring classic tracks like Unskinny Bop, Talk Dirty To Me, Every Rose Has It&#039;s Thorn, Nothin&#039; But A Good Time and more, the band demonstrates what 10 years of hard work can do.
